      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AUSSIE GEM (2) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 2.25 lengths at this track in a handy 22.57 beating Farmer Russell. Form reads well for this. MOO MOVE (4) ran below his best last time finishing eighth (23.35) over 400m at this track in a Free For All. Can figure in the finish. BOLT OF FUN (6) is a handy type who was well below best latest at this track, finishing fourth (28.56) in a OPEN. Generally safe to begin but was always well back last time. Has a good record here at this journey. Has ability and is one of the better chances. SHEERAN MELODY (1) was unplaced here last start but gets his chance to atone.",
